		{"id":"aea4cc65f2142cc6","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentPropsDefinition***\n\n```\ninterface ComponentPropsDefinition {\n¬† style: ComponentStyleDefinition[];\n¬† attributes: [];\n¬† state: [];\n¬† slots: [];\n¬† accessibility: [];\n¬† data: [];\n¬† events: [];\n}\n```","x":-1640,"y":240,"width":760,"height":360},
